Open the Prometheus service configuration file.
sudo nano /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml

Add the Node Exporter as a target in the Prometheus service. Place the configuration at the bottom of the file.
...
- job_name: '<server-name>-node_exporter'
    static_configs:
    - targets: ["<ip-endpoint>:9100"]
        labels:
        hostname: <server-name>

Validate the Prometheus configuration file syntax.
sudo promtool check config /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml

Restart the Prometheus service.
sudo systemctl restart prometheus
sudo systemctl status prometheus
